LanguageData.MSE_AdvancedEndoskeletonStimulator.label: advanced endoskeleton stimulator
LanguageData.MSE_AdvancedEndoskeletonStimulator.descr: An advanced torso implant that stimulates the overall muscles so they can operate at maximum performance. Requires archotech implants surgery research before installing.

LanguageData.AdvancedJoywire.label: advanced joywire
LanguageData.AdvancedJoywire.description: An advanced brain implant that stimulates the brain's pleasure centers. It dramatically improves a user's mood without any side effect. Advanced Joywires are illegal on many worlds, and are known for destroying whole cultures. Requires archotech implants surgery research before installing.
LanguageData.AdvancedPainstopper.label: advanced painstopper
LanguageData.AdvancedPainstopper.description: An advanced brain implant which inhibits nociception, or pain sensation. While it does allow the user to accomplish more, it turns out pain has a purpose. When you don't feel it, you can get hurt really bad really easily. Can be activated or deactivated according to user will. Requires archotech implants surgery research before installing.
